                  Thirdly, to ſmite the earth with all plagues, wherein we have;


1. The agreement between the ſeals opening, and the Trumpets ſounding, and the vialls powering forth, p. 152, 153

2. The ſeven vialls opened, together with the ſeven ſeals, and the ſeven Trumpets, from p. 155. unto p. 169.

